{"tid":2163263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【極右組織】堅信美國有地下政府 虛擬邪教組織「匿名者Q」興起","createTime":"2020-08-18T14:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T14:44:04.000Z","uid":293677,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0cbd9637b5b3fcc1386397985a723870374310ce","tid":2163263,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"2020-08-18 22:00:24<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國近期有一個名為「匿名者Q」（QAnon）的新興右翼組織引發討論，他們的核心教義是堅信有一個由民主黨菁英組成的「深層政府」（deep state）掌握實權，並隨時有可能推翻執政黨政府，因此組織旨在揭發民主黨菁英的陰謀；該組織規模龐大，連現今檯面上的眾議員也是「匿名者Q」支持者。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">綜合媒體報導，匿名者Q是個結構鬆散的網路組織，支持者多數是美國總統川普（Donald Trump）的死忠粉絲，匿名者Q相信，民主黨權貴都是「崇拜撒旦的戀童癖」，他們不僅經營著各種性剝削產業，甚至靠著掌控媒體與娛樂事業，正在密謀推翻川普政府。而組織成員對於其核心教義的堅信程度也讓CNN稱其為「虛擬的邪教組織」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">該組織相信「深層政府」已經串連了國際社會官僚體制，並針對川普及其支持者發起顛覆行動，他們還認為政府中藏有一位軍方或情治出身的極高層人物「Q」，他立志揭發民主黨人的陰謀，因此被支持者視為愛國者或聖人般的存在。</span><br />\n<br />\n而近日受到武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情影響，人們只能隔離在家，鬱悶情緒無處宣洩之下導致匿名者Q的支持者迅速上升，匿名者Q支持者臉書社團之一「匿名者Q新聞與最新消息、信號、麵包屑與對抗陰謀之戰」（QAnon News &amp; Updates-Intel drops, breadcrumbs, &amp; the war against the Cabal），該社團的成員從今年1月1日至8月1日足足暴漲10倍。<br />\n<br />\n美國多家媒體也特別示警，表示「匿名者Q」是一個不能忽視的存在，它可能助長國內的極端暴力主義，目前Facebook也正致力於管控匿名者Q的社群，避免有心人士利用平台滋事。但在官方態度方面，近日川普被問到關於匿名者Q的問題時，卻刻意忽略該題，顯然並無意打擊該社群。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3264201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3264201&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5i%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=f8fcd291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3264201&h=00fd9dce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3264201</a>"},{"pid":"63e4e981091d3d9227e94fcc1e2326bc4cbe22ad","tid":2163263,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a6b6213972d9011c3324eb85d8f66a171351f4","tid":2163263,"uid":4783,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"反民主黨就係恐怖組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔支持民主黨就係極右民粹<br />\n唔洗講咁多野啦"},{"pid":"1b814aac35087e0f4a85699e821fdc3f25cd674a","tid":2163263,"uid":278298,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:26:40.000Z","msg":"所有連登仔都係教徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60b4c0fd098d9716886118f6702495f95b761b4","tid":2163263,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:27:21.000Z","msg":"G持匿名者Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3976650992a3db4ce3f553c65a5e4abdff2f32","tid":2163263,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63e4e981091d3d9227e94fcc1e2326bc4cbe22ad","tid":2163263,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"4chan 係咪即係美國連登?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660f4362ea166f9da260f95560fc40d37214fe63","tid":2163263,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:29:36.000Z","msg":"CNN先報, 第一下就屈人極右<br />\n真係左膠一向做法"},{"pid":"b99d44edeb6291ff24ad3ae3330cfb77a4242a1a","tid":2163263,"uid":61577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:30:17.000Z","msg":"美國不嬲實權都唔係華盛頓<br />\n係華爾街"},{"pid":"99a0b319fb32156e72f49a6ea5af3c8a3123b7c1","tid":2163263,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />控制美國既真正話事人唔係不嬲係「共濟會」咩?"},{"pid":"5d8c9ae42dfb275e10bf8d4f1f15bed076915699","tid":2163263,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"羅特希爾德家族 世界最有錢家族<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9012fc55a07330a82ab010e9f175a158f9a2926","tid":2163263,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"民主黨權貴都是「崇拜撒旦的戀童癖」<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eca3b3b14c07fbbfc0ea145617c571ff30cc4c1","tid":2163263,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9012fc55a07330a82ab010e9f175a158f9a2926","tid":2163263,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"民主黨權貴都是「崇拜撒旦的戀童癖」<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:34:21.000Z","msg":"事實係<br />\n當年3K黨其實係民主黨殘部創立"},{"pid":"14438a47e48968a5b67784fb2a5ec70e9e122403","tid":2163263,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"匿名者Q其中已經出現左好一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985361f174fee628ca77c7bfd9f4ebbf2776512d","tid":2163263,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"匿名者Q（QAnon[a] [/kjuːəˈnɒn/]）是一種極右翼陰謀論[1][2][3][4][5]認為美國政府內部存在著一個反對美國總統唐納&middot;川普和其支持者的深層政府。[6]這個理論是由2017年10月 4chan 討論版中一個署名為Q的匿名用戶發起的，匿名者Q聲稱自己掌握了涉及川普政府及其在美國的反對者的機密信息。此外，Q還誣告了眾多自由派好萊塢演員，政治家和高級官員參與國際地下孌童網絡，他還聲稱唐納&middot;川普假裝通俄，以誘使羅伯特&middot;穆勒暴露出深層政府的存在，並且成功阻止了由巴拉克&middot;歐巴馬，希拉蕊&middot;柯林頓和喬治&middot;索羅斯發動的政變。[7][8][9]「Q」這個名字出自美國機密許可中的最高級別「Q級許可」。<br />\n<br />\n匿名者Q的出現與川普此前一番耐人尋味的言論有關。2017年10月，川普在白宮與記者談話時提到了一場「風暴前的寧靜(the calm before the storm)」，當時有記者追問：「你說的是什麼風暴？」川普語焉不詳地回應：「你會知道的。」這讓在場的記者大惑不解[10]。<br />\n<br />\n這一陰謀論主要由川普總統的支持者以「風暴和大覺醒」的名義傳播，但公眾認為這些觀點是「毫無根據」，[11][12][13]「精神錯亂」[14]和「缺少證據」 的。[15]匿名者Q的支持者被公眾稱為「瘋狂的陰謀論邪教」[16]和「網際網路上最狂熱的一些川普粉絲」。[17]<br />\n<br />\n2018年夏天，匿名者Q的追隨者開始在川普的集會上現身。[18]活躍於電視和電台的公眾人物麥可「萊昂內爾」勒布朗是該理論的推動者，他於2018年8月24日在橢圓形辦公室獲得了跟川普總統的拍照機會。[19] <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E8%80%85Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258C%25BF%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%2580%2585Q&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5i%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=0335927f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E8%80%85Q</a>"},{"pid":"6ea2b4d0097994f3186c41669b92c343409fca87","tid":2163263,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a076b8cfed34dc899235c1b8ff6a673d138ad8d","tid":2163263,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ea2b4d0097994f3186c41669b92c343409fca87","tid":2163263,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:37:32.000Z","msg":"共X會，光X會背後話事人其實係Q<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c7d247ceb30d5d734cd3c050080077bbe0aa1a","tid":2163263,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:44:04.000Z","msg":"表面幫trump ，實則害 trump"}]}